## Authorization

### Permissions

```php
// Automatic permission checks (if setDefaultPermissions = true)
// - {route-name}_view (index, show)
// - {route-name}_create (create, store)
// - {route-name}_edit (edit, update)
// - {route-name}_delete (destroy)
// - {route-name}_restore (restore)
// - {route-name}_forcedelete (forceDelete)
// - {route-name}_duplicate (duplicate)

// Disable default permissions
protected $setDefaultPermissions = false;

// Custom permission prefix
protected function permissionPrefix($permission = '')
{
    return 'custom_prefix' . ($permission != '' ? "_{$permission}" : '');
}

// Check permissions in methods
if (!$this->getIndexOption('create')) {
    abort(403);
}

// Check if gates are active
if ($this->isGateable()) {
    // Permission system is active
}
```

