## Best Practices

### ✅ DO

```php
// Use repository methods
$item = $this->repository->getById($id);

// Check permissions
if ($this->getIndexOption('edit')) {
    // Show edit button
}

// Validate requests
$input = $this->validateFormRequest()->all();

// Use nested scopes
$scopes = $this->nestedParentScopes();

// Return proper responses
return $this->respondWithSuccess('Message');

// Eager load relationships
protected $formWith = ['user', 'category'];
```

### ❌ DON'T

```php
// Don't query directly
$item = Model::find($id); // ❌ Use repository

// Don't hard-code permissions
if (auth()->user()->can('edit-posts')) { } // ❌ Use getIndexOption()

// Don't skip validation
$item = $this->repository->create($this->request->all()); // ❌ Validate first

// Don't return raw models
return $item; // ❌ Use respondWithSuccess() or transformers

// Don't forget eager loading
// Causes N+1 queries // ❌ Use $formWith
```

